    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices for roasting coffee beans, one type consisting of a cylindrical metal receptacle with sealable opening, attached to a long handled rod. This is placed over a fire to roast the coffee beans. For mechanized coffee roasters, typically electric, use "coffee roasting machines."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
